                    <comment id="12540371" author="mreutegg" created="Tue, 6 Nov 2007 08:08:42 +0000"  >Moved methods related to subscriptions to the RepositoryService. This is in line with the already existing functionality, which is all located on the service interface. Subscription becomes a marker interface and allows an implementation to hold proprietary information about the current state of the subscription (e.g. an svn implementation may hold the revision number of the last change reported as events).&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;
Unless someone objects I will adapt all modules in jackrabbit accordingly and commit the changes later today.</comment>
                    <comment id="12540395" author="mreutegg" created="Tue, 6 Nov 2007 10:17:25 +0000"  >Committed the patch and adapted jcr2spi and spi2jcr modules.&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;
svn revision: 592356</comment>
                    <comment id="12540397" author="mreutegg" created="Tue, 6 Nov 2007 10:23:28 +0000"  >Modules in sandbox that depend on the SPI are now also updated.</comment>
